Title: Designates state route 394 in the village of Lakewood, county of Chautauqua, as the "Lance Corporal Aaron M. Swanson Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates state route 394 in the village of Lakewood, county of Chautauqua, as the "Lance Corporal Aaron M. Swanson Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Lance Corporal Aaron M. Swanson Memorial Highway"
